title: Tech concludes Wes Kittley Invite - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech concludes Wes Kittley Invite - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: ABILENE, Texas – The Texas Tech track and field team concluded the Wes Kittley Invitational Saturday evening at Elmer Gray Stadium, highlighted by Aneesa Scott registering a new PR in the 200 at 23.07 – the No. 1 time in the NCAA currently.
